caption.text:
July was BUSYYY but I filmed a bunch of B-roll clips to make this reel! If you need 20 b-roll reel ideas, comment “ROLL” on this reel ❤️

I honestly can’t remember a month where I worked so much or so hard. Busy days, but it’s worth it to see the changes we’re making in people’s lives this week (in the Content Creation Challenge)!
